%% Diagram: Partition Scenario — CP vs AP behaviour
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant N1 as Node A
    participant N2 as Node B

    note over N1,N2: Partition: N1 and N2 cannot exchange messages

    C->>N1: write(x=1) acked
    C->>N2: read(x)

    alt CP system (linearizable)
        N2-->>C: ERROR / timeout
        note right of N2: Sacrifices A to preserve C
    else AP system (eventual)
        N2-->>C: x=0 (stale local value)
        note right of N2: Sacrifices C to preserve A
    end
